      "span_text": "JC-1 can selectively enter mitochondria and reversibly changes color as the Δψm changes.  As shown in Figures 2a and b , there was a significantly increased green fluorescence in cells exposed to t-BHP (80 μM; Po0.05), suggesting that the mitochondrial membrane was depolarized."
